<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Krista chanchin hawih ka muh in,
 Lunggil in pak la sa;
 Kei din a thii Kalvari ah,
 Krista ka la hi hen.

[V2]
 Krista chanchin hawih ka muh in,
 Kipahna la sa'ng ie;
 Kei a ahi, pak la sa'ng ka,
 Krist ka la hi hen.

[V3]
 2. Krista ka Thiempu leh Lalpen,
 Ka Thiemgau vak a dim;
 Thiempu Lien lalchutphah ma ah,
 Thilhihthei, ka Pathien.

[V4]
 3. Amah chuh lalte Lal ahi,
 Lalpente Lalpen chu;
 Amah Felna Nisa ahi,
 Hihdamna kim A nei.

[V5]
 4. Kumsawt guo bang ka hinna di'n,
 Kalvari ah athii;
 Ka gitloh cheng silthien na di'n,
 A thisan a luong ie.

[V6]
 5. Krista Isu kei di'n Bangkim,
 Ka muonna, ka hehpih;
 Lei a ka hinna leh van a,
 Kipahna lallukhuk.</lyrics>
<title>THE PEARL OF GREATEST PRICE</title>
<hymn_number>46</hymn_number>
</song>